channel.title: The 31 with Brandt Tobler
channel.description: Comedian Brandt Tobler spent countless hours crafting 31 of the most unconventional questions designed to go where no credible journalist would ever dare. Listen each week as he probes your favorite celebrities, comedians, rock stars, athletes, and other fascinating citizens of the world for the answers you never knew you wanted to hear. The questions are pretty good...... But the answers are always amazing!
